title: Bug 116564 - Title of Hyperlink Builder changes with settings
description: The title of the hyperlink builder should be 'Hyperlink Options', but it changes with the settings.
OB: When clicking on 'OK' and reopening the hyperlink builder, the actual result is that the title becomes 'www.actuate.com'.
EB: The expected result is that the title of the hyperlink builder should be 'Hyperlink Options'.
SR:
To reproduce the issue: 
1. Set a label hyperlink as 'www.actuate.com'.
2. Click on 'OK' and reopen the hyperlink builder.
